\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Row buffer access scenarios and timeout precharge outcomes. (a)~Three row buffer states at the time of a memory request. A row buffer hit incurs only $t_\mathrm  {CAS}$. A closed-bank access requires $t_\mathrm  {RCD} + t_\mathrm  {CAS}$. A row buffer conflict pays $t_\mathrm  {RP} + t_\mathrm  {RCD} + t_\mathrm  {CAS}$. (b)~Four outcomes of timeout-triggered speculative precharge. CRAFT's feedback loop uses the three outcomes involving a precharge event.}}{5}{}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:timing}{{2}{5}{}{figure.2}{}}
\@writefile{toc}{\contentsline {section}{\numberline {3}CRAFT Design}{5}{}\protected@file@percent }
