\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces DRAM-level performance across 12 workloads. (a)~Read row buffer hit rate. CRAFT achieves the highest RBHR on every workload, with an average improvement of 5.62\% over the best baseline. (b)~Average read latency in DRAM cycles. CRAFT achieves the lowest latency on every workload, with a mean reduction of 2.74\%.}}{11}{}\protected@file@percent }
